\title{Weak universal property for [cpo sums](dt-0031)}
##{
(h \circ \mathit{inl} = f \land h \circ \mathit{inr} = g)\;\; \text{iff}\;\; \scase{f}{g} \sqsubseteq h
}
\p{This property is called \em{weak} because it uses only the [information ordering](dt-000B) rather than equality on the right hand side.}
